<paragraph blockId="198.[151,1120,477,503]" box="[151,1120,477,503]" pageId="198" pageNumber="199">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,1120,477,503]" pageId="198" pageNumber="199">
Key to subfamilies and genera of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1905" box="[567,704,477,503]" class="Insecta" family="Aclerdidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="198" pageNumber="199" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Aclerdidae</taxonomicName>
based on adult male morphology
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
